OL,3,CStarmer denies misleading MPs over
OL,4,CMandelson in wake of new photo
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has denied that he
OL,7,Fmisled MPs when he said the proper
OL,8,Fprocess was followed in the
OL,9,Fappointment of Lord Peter Mandelson as
OL,10,FUS ambassador.
OL,12,FAt a press conference on Monday, the
OL,13,FPM admitted the "process wasn't strong
OL,14,Fenough", but insisted that his
OL,15,Findependent advisors had found no
OL,16,Fevidence that the rules were not
OL,17,Ffollowed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
