CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer denies misleading MPs over
OL,4,CMandelson in wake of new photo
OL,6,FThe PM was also asked whether he
OL,7,Fregretted appointing Lord Mandelson to
OL,8,Fthe role, after ITV News uncovered the
OL,9,Ffirst known photo of the former Labour
OL,10,Fpeer with Andrew Mountbatten-Windor
OL,11,Fand convicted paedophile Jeffrey
OL,12,FEpstein.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer denies misleading MPs over
OL,4,CMandelson in wake of new photo
OL,6,FAt a press conference on Monday, ITV's
OL,7,FPolitical Editor Robert Peston asked
OL,8,Fthe prime minister: "You'll have seen
OL,9,Fthe picture that ITV published of
OL,10,FEpstein with Mandelson and the former
OL,11,FPrince Andrew in their dressing gowns.
OL,12,FWhy, in Jonathan Powell's words, did
OL,13,Fyou rush that appointment, given that
OL,14,FKaren Pierce was prepared to stay for
OL,15,Fa few months and that's what the US
OL,16,Fpresident wanted?"
OL,18,FIn reply, Starmer told ITV News he
OL,19,Ffollowed the rules as they were - but
OL,20,Fconceded that they weren't up to
OL,21,Fscratch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer denies misleading MPs over
OL,4,CMandelson in wake of new photo
OL,6,FHe did not reply on the point of
OL,7,Fwhether he rushed the process.
OL,9,F"In relation to Mandelson, look, the
OL,10,Findependent advisor has looked at the
OL,11,Ftail end of last week at the process
OL,12,Fwe went through and he said it was the
OL,13,Fproper process," he said.
OL,15,F"My reflection is the process wasn't
OL,16,Fstrong enough."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer denies misleading MPs over
OL,4,CMandelson in wake of new photo
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister suggested further
OL,7,F"strengthening" the vetting process
OL,8,Fwill be answer to preventing the same
OL,9,Fmistakes happening again, amid
OL,10,Fquestions over how his personal
OL,11,Fjudgement might have played a role.
OL,13,FStarmer made the comments at his first
OL,14,Fpress conference since the Mandelson
OL,15,FFiles - government documents related
OL,16,Fto the appointment and vetting process
OL,17,Fwhich saw Lord Mandelson be appointed
OL,18,Fas US ambassador - were published last
OL,19,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
