OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer denies misleading MPs over
OL,4,CMandelson in wake of new photo
OL,6,FIn September last year, Starmer told
OL,7,FMPs that the "full due process was
OL,8,Ffollowed" when he was questioned about
OL,9,Fhis decision to appoint Lord Mandelson
OL,10,Fas US ambassador, following
OL,11,Frevelations about the depth of the
OL,12,FLabour grandee's relationship with
OL,13,FJeffrey Epstein.
OL,15,FBut, following the publication of
OL,16,Ffiles related to the appointment and
OL,17,Fvetting process last Wednesday, the PM
OL,18,Ffaced questions about how closely he
OL,19,Ffollowed all the rules in appointing
OL,20,FMandelson to the top diplomatic role.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer denies misleading MPs over
OL,4,CMandelson in wake of new photo
OL,6,FThe documents revealed that Starmer
OL,7,Fwas warned by civil servants that
OL,8,Fthere was a "reputational risk" to
OL,9,Fappointing Mandelson because of his
OL,10,Flinks to Epstein - and pointed to
OL,11,Fnewspaper reports that the former
OL,12,FLabour cabinet minister had stayed at
OL,13,Fthe sex-offenders house after he was
OL,14,Fjailed,
OL,16,FThey also included a note of a call
OL,17,Fwith National Security Advisor
OL,18,FJonathan Powell, where he remembered
OL,19,Fthe vetting process around Mandelson
OL,20,Fbeing "weirdly rushed".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer denies misleading MPs over
OL,4,CMandelson in wake of new photo
OL,6,FThe files also showed that two
OL,7,Fsections reserved for the PM to write
OL,8,Fcomments about Lord Mandelson's
OL,9,Fappointment were left blank, leading
OL,10,Fthe Conservatives to accuse Starmer of
OL,11,Fa "cover up".
OL,13,FITV News understands no redactions
OL,14,Fwere made to those sections, but
OL,15,FStarmer had not filled them in after
OL,16,Freviewing them.
OL,18,FAt the presser, the PM apologised for
OL,19,Fthe appointment and conceded that the
OL,20,Frules weren't good enough - but denied
OL,21,Fthat he had misled the Commons.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer denies misleading MPs over
OL,4,CMandelson in wake of new photo
OL,6,F"The independent adviser looked at
OL,7,Fthat very question, and answered it
OL,8,Fvery robustly - that the process had
OL,9,Fbeen followed," he said.
OL,11,F"The problem was the process wasn't
OL,12,Fstrong enough. But ultimately it was
OL,13,Fmy mistake and I have apologised for
OL,14,Fthat. "
OL,16,FHe added that he was working to update
OL,17,Fthe rules, including adding a ban on
OL,18,Fannouncing appointments until the full
OL,19,Fvetting process had been completed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
